{"title":"Gas 费与 Gwei","uid":"c6285721d3873ba9df2b45fecd80ac7f","slug":"Gas-费与-Gwei","date":"2025-04-07T01:35:33.000Z","updated":"2025-04-07T03:27:38.356Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Gas-费与-Gwei.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/img/gas.jpg","content":"<h2 id=\"gas-费\">Gas 费</h2>\n<h3 id=\"定义\">定义</h3>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>Gas费（Gas Fee）就是你在区块链上执行操作时要支付给网络的“手续费”。</p></blockquote>\n<p>就像你开车需要汽油，在以太坊（或其他链）上“动手”——比如转账、买NFT、铸币、调用智能合约——也都需要“燃料”，这个燃料就是：<strong>Gas（燃气）</strong>。</p>\n<h3 id=\"产生原因\">产生原因</h3>\n<p>因为：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>区块链上每个操作都要全网节点验证 &amp; 执行。</li>\n<li>每个节点都要消耗算力、时间、资源。</li>\n<li>所以得有一个机制来 <strong>激励矿工/验证者</strong>去处理你的交易。</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"概念辨析\">概念辨析</h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr class=\"header\">\n<th>概念</th>\n<th>含义</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr class=\"odd\">\n<td><strong>Gas（单位）</strong></td>\n<td>你这个操作大概需要多少“运算步数”</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"even\">\n<td><strong>Gas Price（单价）</strong></td>\n<td>当前网络上，每个 Gas 单位的价格（通常用 Gwei 表示）</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"odd\">\n<td><strong>总费用 = Gas * Gas Price</strong></td>\n<td>你需要支付的 ETH 或其他代币数量</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3 id=\"计算案例\">计算案例</h3>\n<p>你发一笔简单转账：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>需要 21,000 Gas 单位</p></li>\n<li><p>当前 Gas Price 是 50 Gwei（0.00000005 ETH）</p></li>\n<li><p>那你要支付的 Gas 费是：</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>21,000 × 50 Gwei = 1,050,000 Gwei = 0.00105 ETH</p></blockquote></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"费率概览\">费率概览</h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr class=\"header\">\n<th>操作类型</th>\n<th>大概 Gas 用量</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr class=\"odd\">\n<td>转 ETH</td>\n<td>~21,000</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"even\">\n<td>调用简单合约（ERC20 转账）</td>\n<td>~50,000</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"odd\">\n<td>铸造 NFT</td>\n<td>100,000 - 300,000+</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"even\">\n<td>与复杂 DeFi 协议交互</td>\n<td>几十万甚至上百万</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>Gas 费是由：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>当前网络<strong>拥堵程度</strong></li>\n<li>你愿意支付的<strong>速度溢价</strong></li>\n<li>交易本身的<strong>复杂性</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"支付目标\">支付目标</h3>\n<ol type=\"1\">\n<li>在比特币或者以太坊等区块上：<strong>验证者（以前叫矿工）</strong></li>\n<li>在一些 Layer2 或新型链上：还可能包括协议、基金会的分成</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"常见误区\">常见误区</h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr class=\"header\">\n<th>误区</th>\n<th>正解</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr class=\"odd\">\n<td>“Gas 是以太坊独有的”</td>\n<td>❌ 不是，几乎所有区块链（Polygon、BSC、Solana）都有自己的 Gas 模型</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"even\">\n<td>“Gas 是平台收的费用”</td>\n<td>❌ 实际上是支付给网络维护者（验证者）的</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"odd\">\n<td>“Gas 越贵就越安全”</td>\n<td>❌ 不是，Gas 只是让你的交易早点打包</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"even\">\n<td>“转个 NFT 怎么收我十几刀手续费？”</td>\n<td>✅ 因为调用了合约逻辑、存储变化等，很复杂，确实需要消耗很多 Gas</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3 id=\"节省指南\">节省指南</h3>\n<ol type=\"1\">\n<li>在网络不拥堵时（比如凌晨）操作。</li>\n<li>使用压缩 Gas 的 Layer2（如 Arbitrum、Optimism、ZkSync）。</li>\n<li>一些新链（如 Solana、Aptos）Gas费几乎可以忽略。</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"gwei\">Gwei</h2>\n<p>“Gwei”一词是指以太坊区块链原生代币以太币 (ETH) 的一种小面额。</p>\n<p>Gwei 是以太坊加密货币中使用最广泛的面额之一，常被用来衡量 Gas 价格。简单来说，Gas 是以太坊网络的定价机制，用于计算用户在交易或执行智能合约操作时需要支付的手续费。</p>\n<p>具体来说，一单位的 Gwei 定义为十亿分之一（一纳米）的以太币，即 1 Gwei 等于 0.000000001 ETH 或 10e-9 ETH。反之，1 ETH 等于十亿 (10e9) Gwei。</p>\n<p>此外，根据以太坊 <a href=\"https://www.binance.vision/glossary/github\">GitHub</a><a href=\"https://github.com/ethereum/web3.js/blob/master/lib/utils/utils.js\">的资料</a>，以太币还有其他几种面额，每一种都表示 <a href=\"https://www.binance.vision/glossary/wei\">wei</a>（ETH 的最小单位）的不同倍数：</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr class=\"header\">\n<th style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>单位</strong></th>\n<th style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Wei 值</strong></th>\n<th><strong>Wei</strong></th>\n<th><strong>以太币价值</strong></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr class=\"odd\">\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\"><a href=\"https://www.binance.vision/glossary/wei\">Wei</a></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">1 wei</td>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>1e-18 ETH</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"even\">\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">Kwei</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">1e3 wei</td>\n<td>1000</td>\n<td>1e-15 ETH</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"odd\">\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">Mwei</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">1e6 wei</td>\n<td>1,000,000</td>\n<td>1e-12 ETH</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"even\">\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">Gwei</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">1e9 wei</td>\n<td>1,000,000,000</td>\n<td>1e-9 ETH</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"odd\">\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">Microether</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">1e12 wei</td>\n<td>1,000,000,000,000</td>\n<td>1e-6 ETH</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"even\">\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">Milliether</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">1e15 wei</td>\n<td>1,000,000,000,000,000</td>\n<td>1e-3 ETH</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"odd\">\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">Ether</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">1e18 wei</td>\n<td>1,000,000,000,000,000,000</td>\n<td>1 ETH</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n","text":"在区块链系统中，Gas 费是用户执行如转账、铸造 NFT 、调用智能合约等操作时支付的网络计算资源费用，而 Gwei 则是衡量和支付该费用的常用单位。Gas 与 Gwei 的关系构成了区块链经济模型中最基础且关键的计费机制。...","permalink":"/post/Gas-费与-Gwei","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.6k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Web3","slug":"Web3","count":2,"path":"api/categories/Web3.json"},{"name":"BlockChain","slug":"Web3/BlockChain","count":2,"path":"api/categories/Web3/BlockChain.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"BlockChain","slug":"BlockChain","count":3,"path":"api/tags/BlockChain.json"},{"name":"Web3","slug":"Web3","count":2,"path":"api/tags/Web3.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#gas-%E8%B4%B9\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Gas 费</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89\"><span class=\"toc-text\">定义</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BA%A7%E7%94%9F%E5%8E%9F%E5%9B%A0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">产生原因</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%E8%BE%A8%E6%9E%90\"><span class=\"toc-text\">概念辨析</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%A1%88%E4%BE%8B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">计算案例</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%B4%B9%E7%8E%87%E6%A6%82%E8%A7%88\"><span class=\"toc-text\">费率概览</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%94%AF%E4%BB%98%E7%9B%AE%E6%A0%87\"><span class=\"toc-text\">支付目标</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E8%AF%AF%E5%8C%BA\"><span class=\"toc-text\">常见误区</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%8A%82%E7%9C%81%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97\"><span class=\"toc-text\">节省指南</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#gwei\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Gwei</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Chujun Xiang","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/07/27/pCvHCgU.jpg","link":"/","description":"　金猴奋起千钧棒， <br> 　玉宇澄清万里埃。","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/Trugen","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"hidden":false,"prev_post":{"title":"多任务学习: MMOE 模型","uid":"5f2e864d1b97aa96abca4e22151653bf","slug":"多任务学习-MMOE-模型","date":"2025-04-21T05:14:21.000Z","updated":"2025-04-21T05:28:24.244Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/多任务学习-MMOE-模型.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/img/MMoE.png","text":"MMoE（Multi-gate Mixture of Experts）是一种改进的混合专家（MoE）模型，主要用于多任务学习。它的核心创新是为每个任务引入独立的门控机制（Multi-gate），动态调整不同专家（Expert）网络的权重，从而更灵活地捕捉任务间的共性和差异。...","permalink":"/post/多任务学习-MMOE-模型","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":822,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Machine Learning","slug":"Machine-Learning","count":1,"path":"api/categories/Machine-Learning.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Machine Learning","slug":"Machine-Learning","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Machine-Learning.json"}],"author":{"name":"Chujun Xiang","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/07/27/pCvHCgU.jpg","link":"/","description":"　金猴奋起千钧棒， <br> 　玉宇澄清万里埃。","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/Trugen","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}}},"next_post":{"title":"Hi there!","uid":"ab58292848b10dce6b1c694b6eb9b247","slug":"Greetings","date":"2023-07-27T02:46:39.000Z","updated":"2025-04-05T07:32:57.111Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Greetings.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"text":"Are you watching? Welcome to my website, here I’ll update some blogs and pieces ...","per